<aside class="widget columnist sportsSummaryViewWrapper">
<h1 class="sportsSummaryViewHeader h3 tf1f3">About Scott Burns</h1>
<p class="textBody">
Scott Burns is a syndicated columnist and a principal of the Plano-based investment firm AssetBuilder Inc.
</p>
<p class="textBody">
<span class="tf1f3">Hometown:</span> Dripping Springs, Texas
</p>
<p class="textBody">
<span class="tf1f3">Education:</span> B.S., M.I.T., 1962
</p>
<p><a href="http://www.dallasnews.com/business/columnists/scott-burns/">Archive</a></p>
</aside>
